Don't overmix or use growth serum too many times on one item.

message: Start by using 'growth serum' on basic ingredients to get positive values. Combine 2-3 'grown' items to make a hybrid; 3-animal hybrids seem to yield the highest values. The peak score comes from applying 'mutation catalyst' *twice* to a 'grown' hybrid.
